variables.name: KEY_SYSTEM_GESTURE_EXCLUSION_LIMIT_DP
variables.comment:
* Key for accessing the system gesture exclusion limit (an integer in dp). * *

Note: On Devices running Q, this key is in the "android:window_manager" namespace. * * @see android.provider.DeviceConfig#NAMESPACE_ANDROID

variables.name: KEY_SYSTEM_GESTURES_EXCLUDED_BY_PRE_Q_STICKY_IMMERSIVE
variables.comment:
* Key for controlling whether system gestures are implicitly excluded by windows requesting * sticky immersive mode from apps that are targeting an SDK prior to Q. * *

Note: On Devices running Q, this key is in the "android:window_manager" namespace. * * @see android.provider.DeviceConfig#NAMESPACE_ANDROID
